Special Keys for PlayerPRO
Tools window
+: next pattern
-: previous pattern
ESC: stops
Tab: plays

Piano window
Keys defined in the Piano Preferences

Digital Editor window
Apple Key + click: plays the current selection
Option Key + drag: drags and copies the selection
Arrow left: selects left cell
Arrow right: selects right cell
Arrow up: selects up cell
Arrow down: selects down cell
Return: next line

Classical Editor window
Apple Key + click: plays the current instrument at the current pitch (where you are clicking)
Shift Key + click: deletes the current note or the current selection
Option Key + drag: drags and copies the selection